name: CI Global Quality Dividend Growth Index ETF
longDescription: ETF designed to provide exposure to a broad range of dividend-paying companies with growth and quality characteristics around the developed world, net of expenses. Currently, the Non-Hedged Units of the ETF seek to replicate the performance of WisdomTree Global Quality Dividend Growth CAD Index (the Index) or any successor thereto.
fulldescription: ETF designed to provide exposure to a broad range of dividend-paying companies with growth and quality characteristics around the developed world, net of expenses. Currently, the Non-Hedged Units of the ETF seek to replicate the performance of WisdomTree Global Quality Dividend Growth CAD Index (the Index) or any successor thereto. The ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible, the price and yield performance of a fundamentally weighted index
